{"tid":1271731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無任何人有權指責行動者既決定","createTime":"2019-07-01T07:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T08:42:39.000Z","uid":157224,"like":101,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"46bd92fedaa8f1c2ee84ed4612fb583f4d39338d","tid":1271731,"uid":157224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:22:07.000Z","msg":"首先個首先,一來無大台,二來無所謂既成功經驗者做指揮<br />\n<br />\n大家都咁高咁大,大家既提議都未被驗證係成功,你地憑乜野判斷行動者既行動係錯誤?純粹就係因為唔符合你地價值觀取向?你地既價值觀就代表世界中心?<br />\n<br />\n對於所有無其他辦法既行動者,縱然我唔一定對佢地既所有行動都認同,但我亦都做唔出指責佢地係鬼呢D自私既言論<br />\n<br />\n要記住,做乜都無所謂,但請記住<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">保護自己,懂得撤退</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望並未失去,敬請等到美國國會既真正打救"},{"pid":"fe348f2a42f625f81a0a6ba5f4385b5384b63dd6","tid":1271731,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a28b125ae8b7fe187ad6fb52dd799c485977b0a","tid":1271731,"uid":116074,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:23:01.000Z","msg":"無任何人可以指責林鄭送中。<br />\n因為都未清楚。"},{"pid":"06bb4eac09715bbf0e8a97aa70c0b5a18cf56146","tid":1271731,"uid":51723,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:23:15.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n尊重前線決定<br />\n<br />\n不割蓆 不分化"},{"pid":"b5f5d237334bbe58ef20e60c80a6a8cd12a2e6c7","tid":1271731,"uid":202912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:23:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d28b55c100289931df494cd24189b700b46cefbb","tid":1271731,"uid":247840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"f7ed36b608d85f044cbf9580d0e1378a4113b106","tid":1271731,"uid":247840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9a28b125ae8b7fe187ad6fb52dd799c485977b0a","tid":1271731,"uid":116074,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"